- I did acting

59:03.177 --> 59:04.011
when I was one year old.

1:03:17.164 --> 1:03:18.198
Hello?

1:03:21.569 --> 1:03:22.570
Hello?

1:04:01.008 --> 1:04:02.409
What are you doing?

1:04:05.245 --> 1:04:06.313
Are you there?

1:04:08.415 --> 1:04:11.619
So, this is how it ends.

1:04:11.653 --> 1:04:12.853
Ayar...

1:04:14.955 --> 1:04:16.190
This is not you.

1:04:16.658 --> 1:04:17.925
You have no idea

1:04:18.526 --> 1:04:20.562
how much you mean to me.

1:04:21.395 --> 1:04:23.030
You'll find your way.

1:04:24.031 --> 1:04:26.266
And how brave

1:04:26.701 --> 1:04:32.072
I feel today, because
I was you, for a moment.

1:05:15.550 --> 1:05:16.551
Ayar.

1:05:17.752 --> 1:05:18.952
Ayar.

1:05:52.386 --> 1:05:53.555
Mom?

1:06:18.278 --> 1:06:19.379
Jasmina?

1:06:23.217 --> 1:06:24.384
What happened?

1:06:25.587 --> 1:06:27.187
Is everything okay?

1:06:32.226 --> 1:06:33.293
I...

1:06:35.395 --> 1:06:37.297
just had a dream.

1:06:40.467 --> 1:06:41.636
Are you sure?

1:06:53.280 --> 1:06:54.516
Good night.

1:07:00.387 --> 1:07:01.321
Okay.

1:07:01.723 --> 1:07:02.757
Good night.

1:07:25.279 --> 1:07:27.147
- Ow, ow.
- Jasmine.

1:07:27.180 --> 1:07:29.182
- Where are we going?
- Shh.

1:07:33.220 --> 1:07:35.489
Whoa. Let's go. Come here.

1:07:35.523 --> 1:07:36.724
Come here. Come here.

1:07:59.847 --> 1:08:00.848
Hey.

1:08:01.516 --> 1:08:02.449
Hey.

1:08:10.558 --> 1:08:13.260
You live here?

1:08:13.828 --> 1:08:15.429
It's temporary.

1:08:16.330 --> 1:08:17.632
Only temporary.

1:08:19.299 --> 1:08:20.635
Come. Sit.

1:08:26.741 --> 1:08:27.809
Here.

1:08:27.842 --> 1:08:30.110
I got this for your birthday.

1:08:37.518 --> 1:08:42.657
<i>♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</i>

1:08:43.390 --> 1:08:48.462
<i>♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</i>

1:08:49.196 --> 1:08:55.369
<i>♪ Happy birthday dear Jasmine ♪</i>

1:08:55.903 --> 1:09:00.742
<i>♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</i>

1:09:03.645 --> 1:09:06.614
I'm tired. It's too late
to eat cake.

1:09:09.851 --> 1:09:11.151
Okay.

1:09:14.321 --> 1:09:15.489
You can sleep.

1:09:16.456 --> 1:09:17.491
You are safe here.

1:09:17.525 --> 1:09:19.292
Come. You can sleep here.

1:09:19.761 --> 1:09:21.395
Come. Come.

1:09:24.999 --> 1:09:26.534
There you go.

1:09:27.702 --> 1:09:29.503
There you go.

1:09:30.905 --> 1:09:32.172
Hey.

1:09:40.280 --> 1:09:41.883
I need you to know something.

1:09:47.822 --> 1:09:49.891
I need you to know I'm sorry.

1:09:53.460 --> 1:09:55.395
I'm sorry I wasn't there.

1:09:56.531 --> 1:09:59.232
But I'm gonna be
here for you now, okay?

1:10:13.681 --> 1:10:16.316
I thought I could become a star.

1:10:19.419 --> 1:10:21.354
Someone you would look up to.

1:10:28.495 --> 1:10:29.964
But I was so ashamed.

1:10:36.637 --> 1:10:38.405
Ashamed of myself.

1:10:46.714 --> 1:10:49.550
People talk about love
like it's this...

1:10:52.587 --> 1:10:55.790
great, beautiful, warm thing.

1:11:00.094 --> 1:11:01.796
But love is hard.

1:11:03.731 --> 1:11:05.499
Filled with worry.

1:11:06.934 --> 1:11:08.335
And work.

1:11:12.439 --> 1:11:13.708
And somehow you end up

1:11:13.908 --> 1:11:16.476
hurting those
you love the most, because...

1:11:31.358 --> 1:11:33.360
I just want you to know

1:11:33.393 --> 1:11:34.796
that I love you

1:11:36.030 --> 1:11:37.865
with all my heart.

1:11:39.432 --> 1:11:44.304
And I'm so sorry
it took me so long to learn...

1:11:47.942 --> 1:11:50.377
to see what that really means.

1:12:44.999 --> 1:12:46.601
Hey.

1:12:49.670 --> 1:12:51.371
Good morning.

1:13:07.822 --> 1:13:09.056
Do you like it?

1:13:49.230 --> 1:13:51.933
Come. Come, Jasmina.

1:14:08.282 --> 1:14:10.151
I miss you so much.

1:14:20.995 --> 1:14:22.530
We lost each other.

1:14:24.932 --> 1:14:26.634
I almost lost you, too.

1:14:46.554 --> 1:14:48.255
Oh, my darling.

1:14:52.727 --> 1:14:54.028
You don't have to cry.

1:14:55.162 --> 1:14:57.531
Oh, thank you.

1:14:58.699 --> 1:15:00.167
Thank you, I won't.

