<i>♪ Speak until the dust ♪</i>

1:19:45.553 --> 1:19:50.491
<i>♪ Settles in
The same specific place ♪</i>

1:19:51.859 --> 1:19:54.862
<i>♪ I refused to go ♪</i>

1:19:56.363 --> 1:20:00.401
<i>♪ Drink it
From a cast iron plate ♪</i>

1:20:18.419 --> 1:20:22.956
<i>♪ I remember
